<br>
What I'm getting at with the Honor System is that I don't believe that if a Jade Reaver drops and a level 55 that hasn't even started their epic should get it over a level 51 that is just waiting on that and a few corrupted to finish the epic.<br>
<br>
We need to be honerable in truely stating how far we believe we are along with our epic.  <br>
<br>
I'm about 25-33% done with mine.  Not much.  So, while I would love VS Remains loot or a Jade Reaver, if Tam or Bado or Stormmy are there and need one of them, then Yes they should get it.<br>
<br>
Hope it helps...<br>
<br>
Oh, yea - and I think that HAlflings should get first shot at any epic pieces because they are Uber and have heiry feet.<br>
<br>
~Bas<br>
